<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٩٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">‌الْأَعْمَشِ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/128">‌إِبْرَاهِيمَ </a>، يُحَدِّثُ عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/710">‌الْأَسْوَدِ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">‌عَائِشَةَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَتْ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِنْ كَانَتِ الْمَرْأَةُ لَتُجِيرُ عَلَى الْمُسْلِمِينَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>